Package dataStructure.hashMap

Interface HashMap<K,V>

Type Parameters:
K - the type of keys in this map
V - the type of mapped values in this map
All Known Implementing Classes:
LinkedListHashMap, TreeHashMap
public interface HashMap<K,V>
The HashMap interface defines the basic operations that can be performed on a hash map data structure.
